purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains  urological and perineal procedures.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify urological and perineal procedures . Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include ICD 9 CM codes that represent  urological and perineal procedures.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
